text: Jollibee’s chicken is super crispy and juicy—full of flavor! The fries are crunchy, and the gravy is perfect. A delicious and satisfying meal!
Chicken, burger and fries came out hot and crisp. Gravy is always good. And the pasta was enjoyable!
Best fast food on campus. My favourite Filipino fried chicken. Better than KFC.

I ordered takeaway today but since I was in a rush, I did not manage to check the items. When I reached back to my accomodation, I realised that 2 orders of fries and 1 jolly spaghetti were missing. Its very frustrating that a large part of the order is missing. There is also no contact number or email to liaise with to get a refund. Please advise on how to go about dealing with this matter. Thank you.
Super nice staff and really fast service, got my food 5 mins after i ordered
